<item>
  <title>Simplification of Portrait</title>
  <dc:creator>Pencil on Paper</dc:creator>
  <link>https://morganwastaken.com/artwork/2025-01-12-portrait/</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 




<p>Like in the <a href="../2025-01-08-pear/index">pear exercise</a>, I am simplifying the object of study–in form and in value. The first attempt is on top, while bottom is the second attempt. In the second version, I spent a lot more time on getting the proportion correct. I think slowing down here was more successful.</p>
<div class="quarto-figure quarto-figure-center">
<figure class="figure">
<p><img src="https://morganwastaken.com/artwork/2025-01-12-portrait/IMG_0992.JPG" class="img-fluid figure-img"></p>
<figcaption>First attempt</figcaption>
</figure>
</div>
<div class="quarto-figure quarto-figure-center">
<figure class="figure">
<p><img src="https://morganwastaken.com/artwork/2025-01-12-portrait/IMG_0991.jpg" class="img-fluid figure-img"></p>
<figcaption>Second attempt</figcaption>
</figure>
</div>



 ]]></description>
  <category>simple</category>
  <category>sketch</category>
  <guid>https://morganwastaken.com/artwork/2025-01-12-portrait/</guid>
  <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
  <media:content url="https://morganwastaken.com/artwork/2025-01-12-portrait/IMG_0991.jpg" medium="image" type="image/jpeg"/>
</item>
<item>
  <title>Simplification of Pear</title>
  <dc:creator>Pencil on Paper</dc:creator>
  <link>https://morganwastaken.com/artwork/2025-01-08-pear/</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 




<p>This was an exercise where the object was simplified both in terms of values (i.e., using a limited palette of 5 values), and in terms of lines (only straight lines could be used). I made two attempts at this. The top figure is the first attempt, and the second attempt is on the bottom.</p>
<p><img src="https://morganwastaken.com/artwork/2025-01-08-pear/IMG_0982.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="First attempt"> <img src="https://morganwastaken.com/artwork/2025-01-08-pear/IMG_0984.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="Second attempt"></p>



 ]]></description>
  <category>simple</category>
  <category>sketch</category>
  <guid>https://morganwastaken.com/artwork/2025-01-08-pear/</guid>
  <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
  <media:content url="https://morganwastaken.com/artwork/2025-01-08-pear/IMG_0984.jpg" medium="image" type="image/jpeg"/>
</item>
